OL,3,CNewcastle place Dan Ashworth on
OL,4,Cgardening leave as Man United circle
OL,6,FNewcastle United have confirmed that
OL,7,Fsporting director Dan Ashworth has
OL,8,Fbeen placed on gardening leave after
OL,9,Fhe reportedly telling the club he
OL,10,Fwould like to join Manchester United.
OL,12,FAshworth stepped away from his duties
OL,13,Fat St James' Park while the Red Devils
OL,14,Fformalise their approach.
OL,16,FNewcastle confirmed the development on
OL,17,FMonday after widespread reports that
OL,18,Fhe had communicated his commitment to
OL,19,Fleave on Sunday evening.
