OL,3,CNewcastle place Dan Ashworth on
OL,4,Cgardening leave as Man United circle
OL,6,F"We are naturally disappointed that
OL,7,FDan has chosen to leave, however our
OL,8,Fexciting journey doesn't stop and the
OL,9,Fprocess to recruit a new sporting
OL,10,Fdirector will begin immediately,"
OL,11,FNewcastle CEO Darren Eales said. "We
OL,12,Fthank Dan for his efforts at Newcastle
OL,13,FUnited and we wish him and his family
OL,14,Fwell for the future."
OL,16,FNew Manchester United co-owner Jim
OL,17,FRatcliffe has identified the 52-year-
OL,18,Fold as the man he would like to lead
OL,19,Fan overhaul at Old Trafford and will
OL,20,Fnow seek to agree a deal with the
OL,21,FMagpies.
