OL,6,FThere is yet to be any formal
OL,7,Fcommunication between the two clubs
OL,8,Fbut it is likely that they will both
OL,9,Fseek a quick resolution.
OL,11,FThe period of gardening leave will
OL,12,Fmake up a significant part of the
OL,13,Fnegotiations between the clubs with
OL,14,FAshworth going through a similar
OL,15,Fprocess when joining Newcastle from
OL,16,FBrighton in 2022.
