OL,3,CNewcastle place Dan Ashworth on
OL,4,Cgardening leave as Man United circle
OL,6,FManchester United would have to pay
OL,7,FNewcastle compensation should they
OL,8,Fwish to cut this period short with the
OL,9,FMagpies likely to hold out for a
OL,10,Fsignificant financial package.
OL,12,FEddie Howe has already expressed his
OL,13,Fconcern over the potential for
OL,14,FAshworth to take his inside knowledge
OL,15,Fwith him but also admitted he would
OL,16,Flike things to be sorted quickly.
