OL,3,CNewcastle place Dan Ashworth on
OL,4,Cgardening leave as Man United circle
OL,6,F"I think your concerns are relevant,"
OL,7,Fhe said when asked ahead of Saturday's
OL,8,F2-2 draw with Bournemouth. "I don't
OL,9,Fknow quite how much I can say on that,
OL,10,Fbut I share your feelings.
OL,12,F"It goes without saying that we're
OL,13,Fvery protective of what's ours,
OL,14,Fwhether that's players or staff. If
OL,15,Fpeople do eventually move on to other
OL,16,Fclubs, there's a process to go through
OL,17,Fbefore that is reality.
OL,19,F"At some stage, there has to be a line
OL,20,Fdrawn and things have to move forward.
